{"tid":780253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大灣區】稱中央「只許成功」　劉兆佳：林鄭列席領導小組增港話語權","createTime":"2018-08-15T04:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T07:16:21.000Z","uid":141151,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"bd20ba83d3fd17a48fa8a7f455afdbef18485eca","tid":780253,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:39:44.000Z","msg":"【大灣區】稱中央「只許成功」　劉兆佳：林鄭列席領導小組增港話語權 (12:14)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180815/s00001/1534305304601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180815%2Fs00001%2F1534305304601&d=Dfr5vMQy2Fz3sieZCL%2FyEiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=641ed0b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180815%2Fs00001%2F1534305304601&h=183ab166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180815/s00001/1534305304601</a><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥昨日起訪問北京，今午將以成員身分出席粵港澳大灣區建設領導小組第一次會議。全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">大灣區對中央而言是「只許成功、不許失敗」</span>，故要從高層領導及統籌。他說，香港特首從未參與過中央層面的決策機構，今次可讓香港更好掌握中央和內地城市的想法，增加話語權，中央在協調利益時亦會考慮香港的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n劉兆佳今早在港台節目稱，中央的目標是要讓大灣區走出去，而香港的現代化和國際聯繫可從中發揮積極角色，特首成為小組成員的安排，可確保各城市步調一致規劃大灣區。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，中國擔心香港產業過於狹窄，因此中央近期出台的政策均協助香港發展成創科中心。他認為，假如沒有中央的支持，香港難以獨力完成。<br />\n<br />\n你話成功咪成功lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上海自貿區<br />\n大灣區<br />\n雄安新區<br />\n大西北<br />\n一帶一路<br />\n2025<br />\n人民幣國際化<br />\n<br />\n全部都成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5527d1088d1ba27d76aa808de1413afb20ad193c","tid":780253,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:40:37.000Z","msg":"【貿易戰】怕咗特朗普 傳中國延推「大灣區」計劃<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bunguS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bunguS</a><br />\n<br />\n搵人通知Trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b62b0b7ae3b61f299f1f6a2166f2ea20121177","tid":780253,"uid":3457,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:40:57.000Z","msg":"考慮香港聲音？ <br />\n你講笑炸"},{"pid":"cdfa8b61e9fd48a51d544e3b35593e0cbc1b8b33","tid":780253,"uid":42042,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"改推大媽區獨立"},{"pid":"2346d7d5ca4e99a5bd5cc73ca8770838a37395ad","tid":780253,"uid":531,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:43:13.000Z","msg":"咁多人想做公務員，搬政府總部上去咪得，身體力行支持大灣區"},{"pid":"c424579d195296498ec85ab737526af7f47857cc","tid":780253,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:43:15.000Z","msg":"通常都係生死一博先講到咁 洗唔洗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0fc350e80458ae68d01a85e3d25d24b7e76c14","tid":780253,"uid":197477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:43:26.000Z","msg":"見d自貿區搞唔掂咪直接夾香港落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d5c4f99d8a448684ff08fc3573ff2ba32f44bf","tid":780253,"uid":55628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1b62b0b7ae3b61f299f1f6a2166f2ea20121177","tid":780253,"uid":3457,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:40:57.000Z","msg":"考慮香港聲音？ <br />\n你講笑炸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"發起公投先算啦"},{"pid":"88788ad25c9bbf23a8a31be88fa2360609f39d68","tid":780253,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:44:36.000Z","msg":"雄安區難道又唔係？"},{"pid":"688bde40152c4d1ba4ccc22ff39f91688585146b","tid":780253,"uid":110019,"l